.TP
.B kb
Manage knowledge bases, folders, documents, and files
.TP
.B memory
Manage user memories
.TP
.B agent
Manage agents
.TP
.B agent\-group
Manage agent groups
.TP
.B agent\-signal
Inspect and trigger Agent Signal source events
.TP
.B bot
Manage bot integrations
.TP
.B generate
Generate content (text, image, video, speech) Alias: gen.
.TP
.B file
